{"questionId": "87f513aa-a49e-436a-9a4c-c87bd3101b4c_16", "correctAnswer": "B", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Use the vertex formula", "content": "For $ax^2+bx+c$, the vertex is at $x=-\\tfrac{b}{2a}$: $$x=-\\tfrac{-12}{2}=6.$$"}, {"title": "Substitute to find $f(6)$", "content": "Compute $f(6)=36-72+30=-6$."}, {"title": "State the minimum", "content": "The minimum value is $-6$. That matches choice <strong>B</strong> — <strong>B</strong> is correct."}]}